<paragraph blockId="28.[227,1436,1096,1158]" pageId="28" pageNumber="95">
Species of 
<taxonomicName authority="Korn &amp; Bockwinkel, 2022" authorityName="Korn &amp; Bockwinkel" authorityYear="2022" box="[352,518,1096,1122]" class="Cephalopoda" family="Trigonoceratidae" genus="Trilobitoceras" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" order="Nautilida" pageId="28" pageNumber="95" phylum="Mollusca" rank="genus" status="gen. nov.">
<emphasis box="[352,518,1096,1122]" italics="true" pageId="28" pageNumber="95">Trilobitoceras</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
<taxonomicNameLabel box="[526,631,1097,1123]" pageId="28" pageNumber="95" rank="genus">gen. nov.</taxonomicNameLabel>
with moderately depressed whorl profile (ww/wh ~ 1.65). Suture line with a broadly rounded median saddle.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
<subSubSection box="[227,1274,1197,1270]" pageId="28" pageNumber="95" type="etymology">
<paragraph blockId="28.[227,362,1197,1223]" box="[227,362,1197,1223]" pageId="28" pageNumber="95">
